Susan Bay https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Susan_Bay 0 Susan Linda Bay (born March 16, 1943), also known as Susan Nimoy, is an American actress who portrayed Admiral Rollman in two episodes of the television series Star Trek: Deep Space Nine: "Past Prologue" in the first season and "Whispers" in the second.
